org.jclouds.collect

Class ForwardingPaginatedIterable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • org.jclouds.collect.ForwardingPaginatedIterable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, PaginatedIterable<T>

    @Beta
public abstract class ForwardingPaginatedIterable<T>
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
implements PaginatedIterable<T>
    An iterator which forwards all its method calls to another iterator. Subclasses should override one or more methods to modify the behavior of the backing iterable as desired per the decorator pattern.
    Author:
    Adrian Cole
